{"tid":1642262,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈 星期日全港籃球友誼賽遍地開花！","createTime":"2019-10-09T15:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T15:20:19.000Z","uid":53610,"like":133,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"e30ddb475f53285d41d1f062d47c1c0a064281a9","tid":1642262,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:53:09.000Z","msg":"【和理手足入】NBA事件好好運用至少贏到一個月國際輿論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639013</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n點解要支持NBA的原因我喺依個post講咗，就唔再多講啦，依個真係千載難逢的機會去connect美國人同幫支那撥火<br />\n<br />\n今次開post係活動建議，靈感源自其他巴打的意見，就同標題一樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">全港籃球友誼賽</div></span></span><br />\n眾所周知，香港人係最熱愛籃球的民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信八成人都有過落街場挑波的經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗聲援NBA同美國被赤納粹日漸侵食的言論自由，我哋香港人勢必要企出嚟，拎起屋企鋪塵粒籃波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，嚟返場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">世 紀 友 誼 賽！</div></span></span><br />\n實行以波會友，用運動connect世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能有人會問，點解要打波？打波同聲援NBA有乜關係？<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好 有 關 係！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n運動活動唔止親民貼地，仲可以大條道理聚集人群，最重要係吸引到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理參加</span></span><br />\n<br />\n比賽當日我希望全港手足可以一齊有波衫換波衫，有籃波帶籃波，做觀眾就帶定文宣舉牌，參賽者可以將自己鍾意的球星貼喺背脊取代號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十八區自行協調，揀各自最大的籃球場作為比賽場地，一齊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">全民運動！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下係現場具體細節建議<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n一，啦啦隊觀眾們負責舉牌同嗌口號，唱埋歌都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二，如果夠多人帶籃球，可以將籃球砌成一個&quot;FREE&quot;字，寄意自由歸於運動界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n其他等各位手足諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">#Stand with NBA！<br />\n#Free America！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n正評=諗得過喎撚屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評=垃圾活動 返去再諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8572e8e18ceda85ad83374d4bb08b775ec69b3b6","tid":1642262,"uid":32187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"籃球場企nba人鏈"},{"pid":"c9c31e6e69798d5e8a66d1482aaea7ec2c5f3dc9","tid":1642262,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:59:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e95cacec6346e115f9baaf7e59e6d9fd64bf9de","tid":1642262,"uid":12789,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"Free America ？會唔會唔太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4aecb5c364ad68eb889e04a371eff4f228a5c4c","tid":1642262,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e95cacec6346e115f9baaf7e59e6d9fd64bf9de","tid":1642262,"uid":12789,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"Free America ？會唔會唔太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"自由國度不容赤納粹侵蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe187286324484eede0e53355b3b1da5a85308a","tid":1642262,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e95cacec6346e115f9baaf7e59e6d9fd64bf9de","tid":1642262,"uid":12789,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"Free America ？會唔會唔太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/