/>connect 會唔會好d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:03:31.000Z","msg":"同埋應該stand with morey <br />\nnba只係同意言論自由"},{"pid":"afce4dd5f67418f0142b1cc29c18d88a27c28633","tid":1642262,"uid":295920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:03:45.000Z","msg":"可以一戰"},{"pid":"42d084481d9accc5c4a68f71812e43d42f52450b","tid":1642262,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月10號全民感謝日<br />\nSay YES to yellow shops!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文宣要人、不分化、不被捕、兄弟爬山<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>連登五毛滲透嚴重，大家要帶腦睇post<br />\n最新技倆：煽動最激進/冇底線暴力行為<br />\n另一邊就叫唔好做嘢，乜乜77<br />\n然後推大量呢類post上熱門吸引眼球<br />\n另外，五毛已經識得整文宣，文宣互毆<br />\n總之頭腦要清醒，好易中伏（中過伏</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n國際戰線：Connect世界支持自由民主<br />\n1. @dmorey 撐港被NBA打壓<br />\n2. 香港人Blitzchung撐港被暴雪公司打壓<br />\n<br />\n政府損失：0人，民望、信譽跌至谷底<br />\n香港人損失：2363人+多人曾經活著<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Signature</span>簽名檔：守護香港，深層改革<br />\n抗爭轉型及進化建議：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持久戰拖垮邪惡</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">重要目標：</span></strong>11月24號區議會選舉、香港民主及人權法案、和平勇武後勤文宣議員：各司其職<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">強調：</span></strong>愛港市民、良知、美國制裁、親北京賣港賊、大話精、傀儡、暴政殘害人民、公平公正選舉、為港人服務<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">防範：</span></strong>掌心雷、利誘淺黃淺藍市民、抹黑<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">流水式示威：</span></strong>警察舉旗咪去另一個地方示威，香港咁多地方可以去，佢想捉你，你咪話走緊囉，太多人行得慢好正常，合情合理合法！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">適當武力/自衛反擊：</span></strong>合情又合理！<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>游擊戰？：</strong></span>對抗黑社會/恐怖分子<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">創意活動：抗爭融入生活</span></strong>唱歌比賽？跑步大叫？商場罷買？摺紙？18區和你傾#Shout4HK#諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：文宣！各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化黃色陣營、民主/黃色經濟圈<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭</span><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMdiioB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMdiioB.jpg&h=7e10cb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5w5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=baec6660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5w5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=ec81be7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5w5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=c2b3cfdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.10.09<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓香港示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨、新華社、環球時報、人民日報<br />\n2.誤導：警總救護車、雷射槍、9吋尖刀等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者/黑警：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n11.警察濫權、濫捕、暴力執法、恐嚇<br />\n12.利用親中人士發表「假」權威言論<br />\n13.用盡手段打壓反對聲音<br />\n14.矮化示威者為甲由、yellow object<br />\n15.緊急法：獨裁特首<br />\n諗到再加</span><br />\nSir, my concern is not whether God is on our side; my greatest concern is to be on God's side, for God is always right."},{"pid":"aef1b9a0372f6673b7278a9f7c152e8879a09ca1","tid":1642262,"uid":53610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47cc706e8586b72b55a691e3239cc6d137d57a27","tid":1642262,"uid":46966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2589b04775a4816ab58edbeacefb5f60704d75f3","tid":1642262,"uid":46966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e95cacec6346e115f9baaf7e59e6d9fd64bf9de","tid":1642262,"uid":12789,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"Free America ？會唔會唔太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />connect 會唔會好d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:03:31.000Z","msg":"同埋應該stand with morey <br />\nnba只係同意言論自由"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"其一，morey冇NBA咁形象化，一諗起NBA就係籃球然後運動<br />\n其二，唔重點提NBA點樣幫班支那人撥火，已經想像到單新聞一傳上大陸，班友實嬲到 紮紮跳，又衝出去911洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4551a022230693aa642526c63dae8447cb6b3197","tid":1642262,"uid":182774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆