動日比賽就肯定係由中午至下午，時間上冇衝突<br />\n至於人權法，先唔講係咪星期一過，依家呢個時勢基本上係過硬，但托gphone話齋要正式啓用至少拖到年尾，所以都唔係咩影響因素"},{"pid":"33724ab4eb76f25cb5c2c00a00ec7661cdfa5bca","tid":1642262,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:12:58.000Z","msg":"推到上行程表<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ede42cdf0b67bf0d432013b09138c239456b841","tid":1642262,"uid":279359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:23:13.000Z","msg":"有冇鳳德球場波友？"},{"pid":"0d93d0c8bf600ae8bafd13370668c0f1aee119c1","tid":1642262,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:35:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e045eb4eec07e679218deb7f0e6c91d12bea241","tid":1642262,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:51:58.000Z","msg":"搭單講下，我覺得社區抗爭會係和理的新方向，隨著黑警濫權問題愈來愈嚴重，好似之前嗰啲欠缺嚴密組織的活動好易就會被鳩拉搞散<br />\n唯一出路必定係將抗爭社區化，加深同邨手足之間的聯繫，再以邨為單位策動活動，增加組織性同策略部署的可行性<br />\n為此，針對同一社區之間的文宣工作同埋聯繫活動應該積極考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a16067604659d79f92d6fd5c340158f5288b29","tid":1642262,"uid":141686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T23:27:28.000Z","msg":"推呀！<br />\n要有吸引到國際視線嘅多元抗爭<br />\n希望有獎品<br />\n冠軍可獲made in China 玻璃心獎盃一個(已碎)"},{"pid":"905aaebb04189b2282ee0a2785f2cc7154260375","tid":1642262,"uid":9430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:26:52.000Z","msg":"去維園搞籃球場人鏈 we connect rockets"},{"pid":"275354575252a04f92b0e04fdbf92301f22bfee9","tid":1642262,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:34:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9002b3fa72b6b69652f23817f56569ab21fdf9d5","tid":1642262,"uid":187510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd026215c244875b6bb6dc533fab7ab